  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="7819189">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7819189/" class="title-link">宋史史料笔记</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7819189"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/52317912/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u52317912-18.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/52317912/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">桃之夭夭</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2016-03-20"
      class="main-meta">2016-03-20 03:14:16</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7819189_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  是书P254，陈智超先生共罗列有史料价值的宋人笔记63种，只提供了书目，未写提要，使用起来并不方便，这多少显示了陈先生对笔记这一文体的轻视，当然，还有一些笔记书目，被陈先生打散归入其他分类条目了，比如《建炎以来朝野杂记》归附于基本史料项目下，比如《东京梦华录》《...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7819189_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_7819189_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





